- **How-to resume (line 1075):** "runs all 7 transports"
- **Goals line 31** correctly says "5 high-value transports **beyond** Telegram/Slack" (= 7 total, not a contradiction)

No enumeration mismatch. Slack is explicitly disambiguated as "one adapter family with two modes."

